## Navigation Patterns

### Deep Linking
Handle deep links and app state restoration:

```dart
class AppController extends BaseViewController {
  @override
  void onInit() {
    super.onInit();
    _handleDeepLinks();
  }
  
  void _handleDeepLinks() {
    // Handle initial route
    final initialRoute = Get.parameters['route'];
    if (initialRoute != null) {
      Get.toNamed('/$initialRoute');
    }
  }
}
```

### Navigation History
Track navigation history for analytics:

```dart
class NavigationService {
  static final List<String> _history = [];
  
  static void pushRoute(String route) {
    _history.add(route);
  }
  
  static void popRoute() {
    if (_history.isNotEmpty) {
      _history.removeLast();
    }
  }
  
  static String? getPreviousRoute() {
    return _history.length > 1 ? _history[_history.length - 2] : null;
  }
}
```

### Route Transitions
Customize route transitions:

```dart
getPage(
  name: RoutesName.detailView,
  page: () => const DetailView(),
  binding: DetailBindings(),
  transition: Transition.fadeIn,
  transitionDuration: Duration(milliseconds: 300),
  curve: Curves.easeInOut,
);
```

## Best Practices

### 1. Route Organization
- Group related routes together
- Use descriptive route names
- Follow consistent naming conventions
- Document route purposes

### 2. Navigation Logic
- Keep navigation logic in controllers
- Use route guards for authentication
- Handle navigation errors gracefully
- Provide clear navigation paths

### 3. State Management
- Use bindings for dependency injection
- Dispose controllers properly
- Handle navigation state changes
- Manage deep link state

### 4. User Experience
- Provide loading states during navigation
- Show confirmation dialogs for destructive actions
- Handle back button behavior
- Maintain navigation context

### 5. Performance
- Use lazy loading for routes
- Minimize navigation stack depth
- Handle memory efficiently
- Optimize route transitions

### 6. Testing
- Test navigation flows
- Mock navigation dependencies
- Verify route parameters
- Test error scenarios